## Creating an instant Zoom meeting

It’s also possible to set up an instant meeting. We recommend you [follow the guidance for the platform you’ll be using Zoom on](https://support.zoom.us/hc/en-us/articles/201362413-How-Do-I-Schedule-Meetings-) as the guidance may vary depending on the devices you are using. The basic steps are similar so you can get started with the following.  
  

1.  Get started by [logging into Zoom](https://zoom.us/signin).

2.  Select Host A Meeting to create a Zoom Meeting and select one of the options:  
     
- With Video On
- With Video Off
- Screen Share Only

3.  Select Cancel when the dialog box appears as you will be hosting the meeting using your browser.

4.  Select Join from your browser.

5.  Select Join Audio by Computer.
    
6.  Select the information icon  ![](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pl2qpGS47vz2IUNOIDCtmTT4FrHi8LfuDeB0sSnhPLnd5RRxsU6R8PNWNtZpxfDzKgMDH0Xv1N9RvGjyIGJMoXH4T8UTvtmaYiBL4M7oiP3_yszCpHsoZsqevWkJ3IyT5d4qIBRP) in the top left corner to retrieve your meeting invite information.
